persembahan Dewi juga, kan?

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:39.080
Tuan Sharma, lepaskan sandalmu.

00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:41.280
Ayo cepat lepas sandalmu!

00:04:41.560 --> 00:04:43.000
Jangan mencoba bertindak cerdas!

00:04:43.200 --> 00:04:45.720
Ayo, berikan aku sandalnya!
Berikan padaku!

00:04:45.840 --> 00:04:46.960
Ayo!

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:50.800
Kamu...
- Hei!

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:53.760
Tuan Sharma, kami punya tamu di rumah.

00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:56.920
Kita harus memberkati mereka
dengan bubuk cabai merah.

00:04:57.000 --> 00:04:57.960
Hai!

00:04:58.120 --> 00:04:59.680
Wanita ini sudah gila!  Berlari!

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:01.200
Hai!  Aku akan memberimu... - Lari!

